quoteText: We or our service providers may use clear GIFs (also known as web beacons, web bugs or pixel tags) in connection with our Site to track the activities of visitors to our Site, help us manage content and compile statistics about usage of our Site.
title: The service may use tracking pixels, web beacons, browser fingerprinting, and/or device fingerprinting on users.
